{"code":"","content":"<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p><font size=\"3\" face=\"Calibri\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></font></o:p></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><font size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri\">问题描述</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 21pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><font size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri\">税务局希望你帮他们编写一个征税程序，该程序的功能是：首先输入某公司的年销售额</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">sale</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri\">和税率</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">rate</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri\">，然后程序将计算出相应的税额</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">tax</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri\">，并把它显示在屏幕上。计算公式是：</span></font><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br />\n<font size=\"3\" face=\"Calibri\">tax = sale * rate</font></span><font size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri\">。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 21pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><font size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri\">输入格式：输入只有一行，包括两个数据，即年销售额和税率。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 21pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><font size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-